'''巴瑞·李文森'''（Barry Levinson，1942年4月6日－）是一名美国电视和电影导演、编剧和制片人。知名电影作品有 ''Good Morning, Vietnam'', ''Sleepers'' 和《[[雨人|雨人]]》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://movies.nytimes.com/person/99530/Barry-Levinson |title=New York Times |access-date=2012-01-28 |archive-date=2013-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021134436/http://movies.nytimes.com/person/99530/Barry-Levinson |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=940DE2D91538F935A25751C1A96E948260 New York Times]</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/12/14/al-pacino-barry-levinson-and-buck-henry-team-up-on-a-roth-tale|title=Al Pacino, Barry Levinson and Buck Henry Team Up on a Roth Tale|author=Brooks Barnes|publisher=New York Times|date=December 14, 2009|accessdate=2012-01-28|archive-date=2011-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110811102103/http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2009/12/14/al-pacino-barry-levinson-and-buck-henry-team-up-on-a-roth-tale/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，后者为他赢得[[奥斯卡最佳导演奖|奥斯卡最佳导演奖]]。

==早年生活==
他生于一个[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]犹太裔美国家庭，母亲和父亲分别为是Violet "Vi" ([[married_and_maiden_names|née]] Krichinsky) 和 Irvin Levinson。他们从事[[家具|家具]]生意<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/82/Barry-Levinson.html |title=Filmreference.com |access-date=2012-01-28 |archive-date=2021-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106014527/http://www.filmreference.com/film/82/Barry-Levinson.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/baltsun/access/90838012.html?dids=90838012:90838012&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Nov+20%2C+2001&author=Frederick+N.+Rasmussen&pub=The+Sun&desc=Violet+K.+Levinson%2C+82%2C+homemaker+who+inspired+son's+Hollywood+films&pqatl=google |title=Pqasb.pqarchiver.com |access-date=2012-01-28 |archive-date=2012-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120725055918/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/baltsun/access/90838012.html?dids=90838012:90838012&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Nov+20%2C+2001&author=Frederick+N.+Rasmussen&pub=The+Sun&desc=Violet+K.+Levinson%2C+82%2C+homemaker+who+inspired+son's+Hollywood+films&pqatl=google |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/chicagotribune/access/7852984.html?dids=7852984:7852984&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Oct+21%2C+1990&author=Siskel%2C+Gene&pub=Chicago+Tribune&desc=Living+in+America&pqatl=google |title=Pqasb.pqarchiver.com |access-date=2012-01-28 |archive-date=2012-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023183631/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/chicagotribune/access/7852984.html?dids=7852984:7852984&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Oct+21,+1990&author=Siskel,+Gene&pub=Chicago+Tribune&desc=Living+in+America&pqatl=google |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他毕业于[[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]的[[美利堅大學|美利堅大學]]。后来到[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]从事演员和编剧工作。

== 事业 ==
1988年他导演《[[雨人|雨人]]》赢得[[奥斯卡最佳影片|奥斯卡最佳影片]]、最佳导演、最佳原创剧本和最佳男主角四个大奖。

== 个人生活 ==
他生于一个[[犹太人|犹太人]]家庭。1975年他与合作伙伴、女编剧[[Valerie_Curtin|Valerie Curtin]]结婚，七年以后两人离婚。他之后又与Dianna Rhodes结婚。他的子女有[[Sam_Levinson|Sam]], Jack, Michelle, 和 Patrick Levinson。

他拥有[[巴尔的摩金莺|巴尔的摩金莺]][[棒球|棒球]]队的少数[[股权|股权]]。

目前他与妻子和两个儿子居住在[[康涅狄格州|康涅狄格州]]的Redding镇。

